ET 颜色·HDPE ·PP ·PE ·混合·剔除</span></dd> <div class=\"spec-meter\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span></span></div></div></dl></article></div></div> <div class=\"spec-group spec-group-industrial\" aria-labelledby=\"spec-group-cdw\"> <header class=\"spec-group-head\"> <span class=\"spec-group-tag\">C&D 废弃物处理线</span> <h3 id=\"spec-group-cdw\">Lion One 一体化站</h3></header> <div class=\"spec-card-grid spec-card-grid-wide\"> <article class=\"spec-card spec-card-industrial\"> <header class=\"spec-card-head\"> <span class=\"spec-card-rank\">L1</span> <div class=\"spec-card-id\"> <p class=\"spec-card-model\">Lion One</p> <p class=\"spec-card-tier\">综合破碎与骨料筛分站</p></div> <dl class=\"spec-card-plate\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <div><dt>MFG</dt><dd>蔚澜</dd></div> <div><dt>类型</dt><dd>移动&nbsp;站</dd></div> <div><dt>等级</dt><dd>重型&nbsp;</dd></div></dl></header> <dl class=\"spec-metrics spec-metrics-wide\"> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>处理能力</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">20&ndash;70</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">t/h</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>进料尺寸</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">200</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">mm</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>占地面积</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">35</span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">m<sup>2</sup> · 11.7 × 3 × 3.1 m</span></dd></div> <div class=\"spec-metric\"> <dt>驱动</dt> <dd><span class=\"spec-value\">100<small>%</small></span><span class=\"spec-suffix\">全液压</span></dd></div></dl> <footer class=\"spec-card-foot\" aria-hidden=\"true\"> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-mark\">蔚澜</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>宁波，中国</span> <span class=\"spec-card-foot-sep\"></span> <span>集成移动站</span></footer></article></div></div></section></main>"
